			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002660_0001"/><!--pb/@n='86r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>48 Euston Squ</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">8 August 
<lb/>1865</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Murray</persName>
<lb/>I am sorry that 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> Murray</persName> cannot 
<lb/>come. And I am 
<lb/>much obliged by 
<lb/>your kind offer 
<lb/>to take us up but 
<lb/>we are invited 
<lb/>to come before 
<lb/>3 to luncheon so 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002660_0002"/><!--pb/@n='86v'-->
<lb/>will leave before 
<lb/>you come at 1/4 to 4<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>I leave this with 
<lb/>the servant as it 
<lb/>was past one before 
<lb/>your note came<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>Yours ever </p>
<lb/><p><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
